      <textAnnotation id="sid-A7BF9937-8083-4F47-B1F2-CD2524F62B96" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Technical Return Reserve is an automated posting program which will account for technical return based on a run rate.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-92A762FE-0BA2-4334-A338-FB30D51E3889" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Stock Rotation reserve is to be calculated for Automated posting program which will account for Stock Rotation Reserve based on RMA Stock rotation. This reserve is required to be accounted quarterly for the expected future returns of goods sold to a distributor.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-FB5B8AD9-33D1-4166-9DAD-24C51910FF3F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This object is to specify the functional details regarding interfacing of rebate percentage of gross (R%G) at profit centre level from ECA to S4 HANA. </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-630CAD89-F541-4284-97AB-F41B3744E6BD" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>An automated posting program for accounting reserves for unissued returns credit notes manages the reserves created for unissued credit notes, which are based on return orders.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EFE5D68F-AD65-4928-9B95-DF0BC04193E5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Rebate Returns Accruals- Direct Customer will be an automated posting program which will account for rebate accrual for Direct Customer (Vistex) where in system shall compute Rebate percentage of Gross on the basis of Aggregated Rebate and Gross Revenue Amount.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4D92A90A-6B66-4ADA-AE35-5453913EE4C0" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/a332eaca62b347a18adb9ac9fad43815</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA IP</text>
      </textAnnotation>
